title: Winning numbers drawn in 'Win 4 Midday' game

maintext:
ALBANY, N.Y. (AP) _ The winning numbers in Wednesday afternoon’s drawing of the New York Lottery’s “Win 4 Midday” game were:
4-3-0-9
(four, three, zero, nine)
